data.description: Beautiful Acreage Property In Flamingo Heights Full Of Rustic Character! Nestled on almost 2.5 acres full of gorgeous views showcasing the majestic mountains, rows of Joshua trees, and vast open desert landscape the area is known for. Pulling up you immediately notice the unique style this 2 bedroom 1 bathroom desert escape has to offer. Bringing you a cabin aesthetic full of awesome wood features, this special property isn't like many others you've seen in the Hi-Desert. As you enter the front door of this 1,650 square foot gem you're greeted by Spanish saltillo tile flowing throughout the living space. Walking into the living room you're immediately relaxed and ready to put up your feet while enjoying the cabin vibe! An abundance of natural light flowing through the windows that feature custom casings accompanied with unique rock wall accents, a custom wood door, and efficient wood burning stove make this room one you won't want to leave. The kitchen is fully equipped with plenty of cabinets, dishwasher, stove, refrigerator, built-in microwave, and designed for entertaining opening up to the rest of the floor plan! The large dining room is very spacious and includes a ceiling fan, stained glass windows, and a sliding glass door. Each guest bedroom has plenty of space including their own private doors to the exterior! Now, the primary bedroom will surely please featuring built-in shelving, stained glass windows, sliding glass window to exterior, and wood paneled walls! Just when you think it can't get any better you find the Primary Bathroom! Walking in you find even more custom features you've never seen before. Built in linen nook, gorgeous stone & brick walls, bathtub, walk in shower, dual vanity, and more stained glass windows! In the backyard the perfect spot for BBQ's or outdoor entertaining! Large patio with paver stones, shade trees, and built -in stone BBQ will have you planning your next get together! Additional features include wood privacy fencing, shade trees, wood shed, chain link fencing, built in exterior shelving, and much more! Houses with this much character don't last long so don't wait and come see it today!
